{"id":53712,"title":"[Technical peculiarities of trans-sphenoidal surgical interventions for prolactin-secreting pituitary adenoma].","abstract":"The results of treatment of 84 patients, operated on for prolactinoma, using transsphenoidal access, were analyzed. All the stages of transsphenoidal surgical treatment are depicted in details, beginning from the patient's position on operative table and distribution of the devices in operating room and up to performance of nasal tamponade. There was established the dependence of the surgical intervention radicalism from the tumor topographo-histological peculiarities and from the earlier conducted treatment as well.","date":"2014-02-07","categories":"Endocrine System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24501972","annotations":[{"name":"Adenoma","weight":0.150256,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adenoma"},{"name":"Pituitary gland","weight":0.149429,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pituitary_gland"},{"name":"Prolactinoma","weight":0.108635,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prolactinoma"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.108111,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Pituitary adenoma","weight":0.0961346,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pituitary_adenoma"},{"name":"Tumor","weight":0.0633182,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tumor"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.0276227,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Substance dependence","weight":0.0248395,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Substance_dependence"},{"name":"Sphenoid bone","weight":0.0197357,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sphenoid_bone"},{"name":"Performance","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Performance"},{"name":"Intervention (counseling)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intervention_(counseling)"}